k?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrPizxQ4aNs0&d=ue6trup5EuQkRH4iLOgmif%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=423bb5f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rPizxQ4aNs0</a><br />\n<br />\n睇完上面D片~又見到demo, 又見到教學~仲見到個生產工序~真心介紹得好詳盡~睇完即刻相信呢個係領先美國幾十年既科技~所以唔捻咁多上官網捻住俾錢買:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ntechmotor.com/index.php/shop/motor.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fntechmotor.com%2Findex.php%2Fshop%2Fmotor.html&d=ue6trup5EuQkRH4iLOgmif%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=39c7a9cb\" target=\"_blank\">http://ntechmotor.com/index.php/shop/motor.html</a><br />\n<br />\n俾完錢再禁下佢個網~又發現原來個開發人本身原來唔識物理~係因為得到一D感召而去開發呢套野~所以忍唔住去search下呢位神人~發現佢由耶撚音樂人變成氣車界伽利略既轉變:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gnci.org.hk/gcontent.php?id=499\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gnci.org.hk%2Fgcontent.php%3Fid%3D499&d=ue6trup5EuQkRH4iLOgmif%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=697e19ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gnci.org.hk/gcontent.php?id=499</a><br />\n<br />\n原來一切係因為<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">愛</span></span>, <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為E=MC^2, 而E係愛</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後有冇巴打一齊買番幾隻~轉手出去隨時賣高10倍<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}